  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the project is to evaluate effectiveness of a multidimensional pharmaceutical care
      plan in improving compliance among elderly polypharmacy users at community pharmacy settings.
      The specific objective of the project is to determine effects of pharmaceutical care program
      on medication adherence and persistence among elderly polypharmacy users.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
